</bookmark>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3149018" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="10"><variable id="change_scale"><link href="text/simpress/guide/change_scale.xhp" name="Zooming With the Keypad">Zooming With the Keypad</link>
</variable></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148487" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="11">You can use the keypad to quickly enlarge or reduce the view on your slide.</paragraph>
<list type="unordered">
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3149501" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="12">To zoom in, press the Plus Sign.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3148837" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="16">To zoom out, press the Minus Sign.</paragraph>
</listitem>
</list>
<paragraph role="tip" id="par_id7954954" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">If you are using a mouse with a scroll wheel, you can hold down Ctrl and turn the wheel to change the zoom factor in all main modules of %PRODUCTNAME.</paragraph>
<embed href="text/shared/00/00000004.xhp#related"/>
